From: Anders Hasselqvist <hassel@xxx.xxx.xxx>
Date: 04-23-99 17:07:58
Subject: @{b}Re: BZIP for vbcc@{ub}

From: Luiz Gustavo Castelan

> again 8), anyone could tell me where to get bzip2 uncompressor for AMIGA?
> I really need this to unpack my VBCC thingy
> 

You can get a version from aminet
bzip2-0.9.0b.lha   util/pack

for example:
ftp.sunet.se/pub/aminet/util/pack/bzip2-0.9.0b.lha


If it is the vbcc compiler you want you can get it from Volker's homepage.
http://www.franken.de/users/vb/vbcc/

Bye,
Anders Hasselqvist
hassel@acc.umu.se

@ENDNODE
