@NODE "Mail_86" " Re: New C user "
From: John Niclasen <Niclasen@bigfoot.com>
Date: 04-29-99 00:23:05
Subject: @{b}Re: New C user@{ub}

From: John Niclasen <Niclasen@bigfoot.com>

On 28-Apr-99, Christoph Krakowski wrote:

> Which language you use depends only on your opinion. But
> there are some large Projects where it is better to
> porgramm in OO, especially if you are working in a large
> team.
