Hardware bang like this:

#define poke(a, b) [1m((UBYTE [0m)a)=b

[3m[1m Do this at the beginning of your program [0m
poke(0xbfe301, 0xff); [3m[1m all bits to output [0m

[3m[1m Do this to send a new value to the parallel-port [0m
poke(0xbfe101, value);

/Jonas

