@NODE "Mail_133" " String handling in C "
From: Mike Carter <mike.carter@xxxxxxx.xxxx>
Date: 04-21-99 21:35:37
Subject: @{b}String handling in C@{ub}

For people moving from Blitz2 or another basic language and are
already missing the string functions such as Instr, String, upper,
lower etc.  then take a look at "GatewayLibrary.lha" on Aminet which
contains all these string operations and more for people who can't be
bothered to write their own for every program that needs them!

Dinky do,


Mike.

